in those organizations that get to predictable

00:40:16.610 --> 00:40:21.150
success is that although they wouldn't use
this terminology, these three managements

00:40:21.150 --> 00:40:26.710
styles which are highly visceral management
styles get added to, get complimented by a

00:40:26.710 --> 00:40:32.370
