00:49:31.990 --> 00:49:36.470
because in treadmill, hiring becomes an amplifier.
Essentially what's happening in treadmill

00:49:36.470 --> 00:49:42.770
is that the 'P' mindset is running first and
foremost. And so we start to hire people that

00:49:42.770 --> 00:49:49.000
got a 'P' preponderance who will confirm,
